// The universe of &ldquo;fake news&rdquo; is much larger than simply false news stories. Some stories may have a nugget of truth, but lack any contextualizing details. They may not include any verifiable facts or sources. Some stories may include basic verifiable facts, but are written using language that is deliberately inflammatory, leaves out pertinent details or only presents one viewpoint. &quot;Fake news&quot; exists within a larger ecosystem of mis- and disinformation. //<br />
