有人回應&rdquo;I am a little sad that opinion and satire, types of writing that can make the real more digestible or understandable in a context, fall into the same bucket as deceptive or misleading or hateful. But I understand the challenge and I appreciate your persistence in creating something of value.&rdquo;<br />
作者就咁樣講&rdquo;I am to, and it certainly doesn&rsquo;t have to stay that way. Given enough examples, you might be able to separate them out.<br />
By the way, Satire/Onion articles are what saved me from going completely mad I think.&rdquo;

